column2: SELECT p.obj, str (p.ra, #, #) as ra, str (p.dec, #, #) as dec, p.r, p.u, p.g, p.i, p.z, str (p.u - p.g, #, #) as ugModelColor, str (p.g - p.r, #, #) as grModelColor, str (p.r - p.i, #, #) as riModelColor, str (p.i - p.z, #, #) as izModelColor, p.dered_g, p.dered_i, p.dered_r, p.dered_u, c.kcorrG, c.kcorrI, c.kcorrR, c.kcorrU, IS# (s.z, #) as z, IS# (s.zErr, #) as zErr, c.z, c.zErr, c.photoErrorClass into mydb.ZW2#_f from Galaxy as p left outer join SpecObj as s on p.objID = s.bestObjID join dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (#, #, #) as b on b.objID = p.objID join Photoz as c on c.objID = p.objID WHERE p.g < # AND p.r < # AND p.i < # AND p.z < # AND c.z > # AND c.z < # AND (c.photoErrorClass BETWEEN # AND #)
